        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Powerful muscles anchor your beak, enabling you to take devastating bites out of any target you can immobilize. You gain a beak unarmed attack that deals @Damage[1d8[slashing]] damage. Your beak is in the brawling group and has the backstabber, grapple, razing, and unarmed traits. However, the beak is awkward to deploy as a weapon. You take a –2 circumstance penalty to beak Strikes against targets that aren't @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Grabbed], helpless, @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Prone], or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Restrained]. Even if an effect increases your melee reach, your beak's reach can't exceed 5 feet.</p>"
        },
